              <p class="text-white leading-relaxed text-sm">
                Organizations typically achieve 200-400% ROI within 12-18 months from comprehensive automation use cases, with healthcare and legal industries showing highest returns due to reduced administrative overhead and improved compliance efficiency.
              </p>
            </div>
            
