              <h3 class="font-bold text-primary mb-2 text-sm">How long does implementation take for industry-specific automation use cases?</h3>
              <p class="text-white leading-relaxed text-sm">
                Implementation timelines vary by complexity: simple departmental use cases (4-8 weeks), cross-departmental implementations (3-4 months), enterprise-wide transformation (6-12 months), depending on industry compliance requirements and system integrations.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="glass-morphism p-4 rounded-xl">
